                industry trends.
                <br />

                My focus lies in crafting exceptional user experiences through
                clean design, intuitive navigation, and optimal performance.
                Eager to innovate and dedicated to continuous learning, I am
                confident that my web development skills will continue to
                evolve. I'm keen on collaborating with fellow developers and
                gaining hands-on experience to tackle real-world challenges in
                the field.
              </p>
            </div>

            <div class="contactcv">
              <div class="contact">
                <a class="btn btn-primary" href="/contact">Contact</a>
              </div>

              <div class="cv">
                <a
                  class="btn "
                  href="../assets/document/CV Jafar.pdf"
                  download
                >Download CV
                  <i class="bi bi-download"></i></a>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="socmed">
              <a
                class="btn"
                href="https://www.instagram.com/jfr.xd"
                target="_blank"
              >
                <i class="bi bi-instagram"></i>
              </a>

              <a
                class="btn"
                href="https://www.facebook.com/jafar.abd.77"
